{"tid":743314,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"離地反共害港","createTime":"2018-07-15T10:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T12:03:47.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec005d40b08e1f8054b75d66d64932146631cfe","tid":743314,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"知彼知己，百戰不殆<br />\n知彼知己，百戰不勝<br />\n<br />\n真心想問一下<br />\n作為一個連登的反共人<br />\n經常參與或搞政治社運的人<br />\n<br />\n請問你一年去左幾多次大陸<br />\n<br />\n如果未能知共，又點能反共<br />\n<br />\n離地反共，只會害港<br />\n<br />\n一年平均上大陸唔超過10次的，又反苂的，都係離地反共撚<br />\n<br />\n反共不如知共<br />\n<br />\n反共之前，請先知共"},{"pid":"22a77e7a98c443e5cba3a020e146f5bc4953f191","tid":743314,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知彼知己，百戰不殆<br />\n知彼知己，百戰不勝<br />\n<br />\n真心想問一下<br />\n作為一個連登的反共人<br />\n經常參與或搞政治社運的人<br />\n<br />\n請問你一年去左幾多次大陸<br />\n<br />\n如果未能知共，又點能反共<br />\n<br />\n離地反共，只會害港<br />\n<br />\n一年平均上大陸唔超過10次的，<span style=\"color: red;\">又反中反共的</span>，都係離地反共撚。<br />\n<br />\n反共，不如知共。<br />\n<br />\n反共之前，請先知共</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7df99640e6f3563aa8d64af7afede241d022a89d","tid":743314,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"離地反共撚，係邊度認識中共和港共<br />\n<br />\n答案係報紙，港報<br />\n<br />\n所以只係本地反共派報紙的傳聲筒<br />\n<br />\n在以鵝傳鵝效應下，比傳媒自身反共更離地。<br />\n<br />\n只有真正經常接觸香港，中共，中國的人，先有資格反共。"},{"pid":"f611b122e4f747f931f127a5b209997a0f81b85f","tid":743314,"uid":52844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T10:50:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無錯，一定要先知共，只去過廣東省都唔算知共，未去過中國23個省都冇資格反共</span>"},{"pid":"2a77efd8eead27e1898ba5cd3d1435722b6260f6","tid":743314,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f611b122e4f747f931f127a5b209997a0f81b85f","tid":743314,"uid":52844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T10:50:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無錯，一定要先知共，只去過廣東省都唔算知共，未去過中國23個省都冇資格反共</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"好多反共撚連深圳/珠海/廣州都冇乜點去過，甚至冇回鄉證"},{"pid":"f2d01859930f4758007eed7870738bc492fecb4e","tid":743314,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"無回鄉證點去？"},{"pid":"93445bacba37a5f291ddd17d933b3857aabd2c2d","tid":743314,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2d01859930f4758007eed7870738bc492fecb4e","tid":743314,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"無回鄉證點去？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T12:03:17.000Z","msg":"申請"},{"pid":"1222bb5d4fffd446bf27f0384394af1215d699cc","tid":743314,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93445bacba37a5f291ddd17d933b3857aabd2c2d","tid":743314,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2d01859930f4758007eed7870738bc492fecb4e","tid":743314,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"無回鄉證點去？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T12:03:17.000Z","msg":"申請"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T12:03:47.000Z","msg":"不了"}]}